@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 2-1. 시나리오 준비: CREATOR 회원가입
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "course-creator-{{$uuid}}@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Course Creator",
  "role": "CREATOR"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("courseScenarioCreatorToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

### 2-2. Course 생성: 생성 직후 DRAFT
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{courseScenarioCreatorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Course 상태 전이 시나리오 {{$timestamp}}",
  "description": "DRAFT에서 OPEN, CLOSED로 전이되는 흐름을 확인합니다.",
  "price": 10000.00,
  "capacity": 5,
  "enrollmentStartAt": "2030-06-01T10:00:00",
  "enrollmentEndAt": "2030-06-10T18:00:00",
  "courseStartAt": "2030-06-15T10:00:00",
  "courseEndAt": "2030-07-15T18:00:00"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("courseScenarioCourseId", response.body.data.id);
%}

### 2-3. Course 수동 OPEN: 모집 시작은 현재 시각, 모집 마감은 요청값
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/{{courseScenarioCourseId}}/open
Authorization: Bearer {{courseScenarioCreatorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enrollmentEndAt": "2030-06-10T18:00:00"
}

### 2-4. OPEN Course 상세 조회: occupiedCount 확인
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/{{courseScenarioCourseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{courseScenarioCreatorToken}}

### 2-5. Course 목록 조회: 상태 필터 OPEN
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/courses?status=OPEN&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{courseScenarioCreatorToken}}

### 2-6. Course 수동 CLOSED
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/{{courseScenarioCourseId}}/close
Authorization: Bearer {{courseScenarioCreatorToken}}

### 2-7. CLOSED Course 상세 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/{{courseScenarioCourseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{courseScenarioCreatorToken}}
